Master, I'm not cunning.

72
00:04:18,317 --> 00:04:20,637
I've behaved lately.
Don't complain about me to Mother.

73
00:04:20,798 --> 00:04:22,358
Keling, don't misunderstand me.

74
00:04:22,358 --> 00:04:23,678
I'm on your side.

75
00:04:24,558 --> 00:04:28,397
You've been doing
great deeds of chivalry all along.

76
00:04:28,718 --> 00:04:30,757
It's very good. I should learn from you.

77
00:04:31,837 --> 00:04:33,118
Learn from me?

78
00:04:33,277 --> 00:04:36,718
Look, when the heroes

79
00:04:36,798 --> 00:04:39,598
see the rise and fall of the world
as their own responsibility,

80
00:04:39,637 --> 00:04:41,238
they're bound to
have some bruises, right?

81
00:04:41,277 --> 00:04:43,277
And they will have
internal or external injuries, right?

82
00:04:43,598 --> 00:04:44,598
So, I hope that you can

83
00:04:44,678 --> 00:04:46,837
bring these heroes to the pharmacy.

84
00:04:47,118 --> 00:04:48,598
I'll treat their wounds,

85
00:04:48,957 --> 00:04:51,678
which is also a small contribution
to your world of martial arts.

86
00:04:52,118 --> 00:04:53,598
I didn't expect that you are also

87
