a man of the martial world.

88
00:04:55,678 --> 00:04:58,238
- It's my duty.
- As I am Heroine in Jianglin,

89
00:04:58,277 --> 00:05:00,718
why don't you call yourself
Pharmacist Hero in Jianglin?

90
00:05:01,957 --> 00:05:03,197
No need.

91
00:05:03,277 --> 00:05:04,998
Master, you need a title.

92
00:05:05,038 --> 00:05:05,957
When you do good deeds,

93
00:05:05,998 --> 00:05:07,798
people will know your name,
which is only fair.

94
00:05:07,957 --> 00:05:09,558
Well, I do good deeds
without leaving my name.

95
00:05:09,637 --> 00:05:11,517
As long as they leave the money.

96
00:05:11,517 --> 00:05:13,757
Money? You still want money?

97
00:05:14,678 --> 00:05:16,038
The pharmacy hasn't been doing well.

98
00:05:16,118 --> 00:05:18,238
You have to help me and the family.

99
00:05:19,837 --> 00:05:21,158
Master, you'd better not call yourself

100
00:05:21,197 --> 00:05:23,238
Pharmacist Hero in Jianglin,
but Piggy Bank Hero in Jianglin.

101
00:05:24,038 --> 00:05:26,718
Discount. Ten percent off?
Twenty percent off? How is it?

102
00:05:35,277 --> 00:05:36,896
Hey, you.

103
00:05:37,718 --> 00:05:38,998
Make me a cup of tea

104
00:05:39,038 --> 00:05:42,118
of goji berry, red date, lily, longan,
and lotus seed. Bring it to my room.

105
00:05:43,038 --> 00:05:44,077
Do you mean porridge?

106
00:05:46,238 --> 00:05:47,877
What did you say?

107
00:05:47,877 --> 00:05:49,757
I haven't finished doing the laundry.

108
00:05:49,757 --> 00:05:50,598
So?

109
00:05:50,957 --> 00:05:51,798
I'm busy.

110
00:05:51,877 --> 00:05:52,918
So?

111
00:05:53,558 --> 00:05:55,277
So, can't you make a cup of it yourself?

112
00:05:55,317 --> 00:05:56,877
Are you a servant or am I?

113
00:05:57,038 --> 00:05:58,598
Time for real action.

114
