I won't wash anymore.

115
00:06:10,837 --> 00:06:14,238
Hey, scrape the bottom of the wok later.

116
00:06:14,397 --> 00:06:15,837
What's the point of cleaning the bottom?

117
00:06:16,358 --> 00:06:19,397
What do you know?
The ash is a medicinal ingredient.

118
00:06:22,358 --> 00:06:24,038
Haven't you done yet?

119
00:06:24,197 --> 00:06:25,598
What have you been doing all this time?

120
00:06:25,757 --> 00:06:27,397
I-I've been washing all the time.

121
00:06:27,397 --> 00:06:28,877
And you haven't finished yet?

122
00:06:29,277 --> 00:06:30,558
So much of it.

123
00:06:32,038 --> 00:06:33,598
So?

124
00:06:33,598 --> 00:06:34,678
So?

125
00:06:34,678 --> 00:06:35,957
So I'm not cooking your meal.

126
00:06:36,437 --> 00:06:38,400
No. I...

127
00:06:41,837 --> 00:06:42,837
Remember to scrape the bottom.

128
00:06:49,991 --> 00:06:51,199
(Lord Ling's Mansion)

129
00:06:52,718 --> 00:06:56,960
Your Highness. Your Highness?

130
00:06:57,158 --> 00:06:58,317
He might still be sleeping.

131
00:07:02,397 --> 00:07:05,517
Your Highness, it's me, Tengyun.

132
00:07:08,437 --> 00:07:10,277
Why do I have a bad feeling?

133
00:07:10,757 --> 00:07:12,704
No way.

134
00:07:17,517 --> 00:07:20,837
Your Highness? Your Highness?

135
00:07:23,197 --> 00:07:24,877
Look. I knew it.

136
00:07:25,757 --> 00:07:27,598
Young Lord, here is a letter.

137
00:07:35,038 --> 00:07:38,158
I'll be out for a few days.
Don't forget our deal.

138
00:07:39,837 --> 00:07:41,837
Brother, can you do me another favor?

139
00:07:42,077 --> 00:07:43,077
What is it?

140
00:07:43,077 --> 00:07:45,158
I might go out often in the future.

141
00:07:45,358 --> 00:07:47,678
Please cover for me. Don't tell others.

142
00:07:49,238 --> 00:07:51,277
It seems that Fourth Prince

143
00:07:51,397 --> 00:07:52,877
still doesn't trust us, huh?

144
00:07:52,998 --> 00:07:54,718
If something happens to him outside,

145
00:07:54,757 --> 00:07:56,317
what am I supposed to do then?

146
00:07:56,517 --> 00:07:58,877
Young Lord, this time
he chose to go out on his own.

147
00:07:58,877 --> 00:07:59,957
It's none of our business.

148
00:08:00,238 --> 00:08:01,158
You fool.

149
00:08:01,238 --> 00:08:03,517
Do you want Father to blame me
for not protecting him properly?

150
00:08:03,517 --> 00:08:05,517
Then we should
go explain to His Highness now.

151
00:08:05,598 --> 00:08:08,837
Fool. Do you want Fourth Prince
to blame me for disobeying the order?

152
00:08:09,792 --> 00:08:11,118
T-Then, what should we do?

153
00:08:11,118 --> 00:08:12,837
What should we do?
Hurry up and find him!

154
00:08:12,837 --> 00:08:13,678
Guards!

155
00:08:13,678 --> 00:08:15,277
Do you know what a covert mission is?

156
00:08:15,277 --> 00:08:16,158
There you off!

157
00:08:16,158 --> 00:08:17,038
