You dare touch my bro...

701
00:33:13,277 --> 00:33:14,158
You started it first.

702
00:33:19,277 --> 00:33:21,517
Boss, why do you have
a hammer on your head?

703
00:33:22,277 --> 00:33:23,797
Boss, you're bleeding from the head.

704
00:33:24,317 --> 00:33:26,398
Mr. Wang said, if you bleed again,
you should go see him.

705
00:33:26,438 --> 00:33:28,238
Yeah, I need to see the doctor.

706
00:33:28,277 --> 00:33:29,317
Don't leave if you are a man.

707
00:33:29,478 --> 00:33:31,198
- Continue.
- Boss, don't be impulsive.

708
00:33:32,357 --> 00:33:33,757
The mountains and
the water will not move.

709
00:33:33,797 --> 00:33:35,037
But people move.

710
00:33:35,117 --> 00:33:36,597
If people don't move, I'll move.

711
00:33:37,198 --> 00:33:38,398
You move. You move.

712
00:33:39,357 --> 00:33:40,317
Go, go, go.

713
00:33:40,317 --> 00:33:41,797
- A-Si.
- Are you alright?

714
00:33:41,878 --> 00:33:43,757
A-Si, A-Si.

715
00:33:45,878 --> 00:33:46,878
Don't leave!

716
00:33:57,438 --> 00:34:02,198
Master, there's something
I really don't understand.

717
00:34:02,517 --> 00:34:03,438
What's that?

718
00:34:07,398 --> 00:34:09,717
Did you really give
Mrs. Chun ninety percent?

719
00:34:11,717 --> 00:34:15,237
Young man, are you really a beggar?

720
00:34:27,758 --> 00:34:28,958
Your quilt.

721
00:34:29,878 --> 00:34:30,838
Given by Mrs. Chun.

722
00:34:37,717 --> 00:34:39,597
She seems to care about you a lot.

723
00:34:39,998 --> 00:34:42,117
Yes. I behaved well.

724
00:34:47,918 --> 00:34:49,077
Why did you turn away?

725
00:34:49,798 --> 00:34:51,758
Nothing. Good night.

